https://angular.io/guide/quickstart


1) npm install -g @angular/cli
2) Code . to be able to open the project in the current folder
3) to compile the Project  ng serve
4) to install Bootstrap npm install bootstrap --save
5)To add a component ----> ng generate component  x
6)To add a service ---> ng generate service x
7)if devit package is not recognized ---->npm install --save-dev @angular-devkit/build-angular
8) to generate the Angulat guard for route guards --> ng g g auth
9) to setup bootstrap css and js with CLI ----> a)npm install --save @ng-bootstrap/ng-bootstrap
                                                b)import {NgbModule} from '@ng-bootstrap/ng-bootstrap';
                                   @ngModule    c) imports: [NgbModule.forRoot()]
                           in angular.json file  d) Styles-->   "./node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"

